properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued January 24 at 4:10AM CST until January 24 at 12:00PM CST by NWS Des Moines IA
properties.description:
...Light to at Times Moderate Snow Continues Over Eastern into
Parts of Central Iowa This Morning...

.Low pressure in Missouri has spread snow over eastern into south
central Iowa this morning with snow totals generally between
3 and 4 inches by sunrise this morning. Though little wind is
anticipated, roads will be impacted during the morning commute.

* WHAT...Snow. Additional snow accumulations of one to three
inches expected.

* WHERE...South Central Iowa.

* WHEN...Until noon CST today.

* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery and snow covered road conditions.
The hazardous conditions will impact the morning commute.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

The latest road conditions for the state you are calling from can
be obtained by calling 5 1 1.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL NOON CST TODAY
